    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称中国态度软化，珍珠奶茶制造商重拾 IPO 雄心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/bubble-tea-makers-revive-ipo-ambitions-with-china-said-to-be-softening-stance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象显示北京方面正在放松对市场的控制，且在业内最大的连锁店之一在今年早些时候的首次公开募股 (IPO) 中表现令人失望之后，市场情绪正在好转，这令中国的珍珠奶茶制造商重启首次公开募股 (IPO) 计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/bubble-tea-makers-revive-ipo-ambitions-with-china-said-to-be-softening-stance</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 05:25:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
